 case\">Accusative</a>\n</th>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la acc|s-form-of origin-&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x113;s\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/idololatren#Latin\" title=\"idololatren\">&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x113;n</a></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la acc|p-form-of origin-&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x113;s\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/idololatras#Latin\" title=\"idololatras\">&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x101;s</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"case-header\"><a href=\"/wiki/ablative_case\" title=\"ablative case\">Ablative</a>\n</th>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la abl|s-form-of origin-&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x113;s\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/idololatre#Latin\" title=\"idololatre\">&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x113;</a></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la abl|p-form-of origin-&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x113;s\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/idololatris#Latin\" title=\"idololatris\">&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x12B;s</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"case-header\"><a href=\"/wiki/vocative_case\" title=\"vocative case\">Vocative</a>\n</th>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la voc|s-form-of origin-&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x113;s\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/idololatre#Latin\" title=\"idololatre\">&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x113;</a></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"form-cell\"><span class=\"Latn form-of lang-la voc|p-form-of origin-&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatr&#x113;s\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/idololatrae#Latin\" title=\"idololatrae\">&#x12B;d&#x14D;lolatrae</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table><h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Related_terms\">Related terms</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=idololatres&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Related terms\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h4><div class=\"deri